      "pinned": 2,
      "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>Adapted from a Zhihu pin: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/pin/2033491876934833059\">54.6k Star、9k Fork，这个项目用12节课教你从0造出Claude Code同款引擎</a>, by @代码科小土豆. Rights belong to the original author. Related column: <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2033490899401957920\">full article (Chinese)</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I spotted a repo on GitHub Trending called <strong>learn-claude-code</strong>. The opening line stopped me cold:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Agency — the ability to perceive, reason, and act — comes from model training, not from external code orchestration.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>That line punctures a multi‑billion‑dollar illusion in the AI world over the past two years: products that wire an LLM API together with if‑else branches and node graphs and call it an “Agent.” The README is even sharper:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What they build is a Rube Goldberg machine... That is not an agent. That is a shell script with delusions of grandeur.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>What the project is about</h2>\n<p>The project’s core pitch is <strong>12 progressive sessions</strong> that walk you through building a miniature <strong>AI Agent engine</strong> by hand. Five historical milestones support the claim that <em>intelligence comes from training, not coding</em>, and the conclusion is:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Agency — the ability to perceive, reason, and act — is trained, not coded.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Harness engineers: the model drives; you build the car</h2>\n<p>The setup leads to one point: as a <strong>Harness engineer</strong>, your job is not to program intelligence into the model, but to build the world the model can live in.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <strong>model</strong> is the driver</li>\n<li>The <strong>Harness</strong> is the vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The project never breaks that rule: 12 sessions add 12 mechanisms, and <strong>the core loop never changes by a single line</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2cc60b32ac81d2f4cf5d3651be5f8b4d.jpg\" alt=\"learn-claude-code screenshot 1\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9c863af0408c5e38a1d57d0600bef5ab.jpg\" alt=\"learn-claude-code screenshot 2\"></p>\n"
